<p>Both the lower and upper towns boast a number of historic buildings, whilst a cable-car can take you up the Pfänder mountain for some stunning views. As well as good local bus service and excellent railway links to the surrounding area, lake steamers regularly cruise the waters, stopping at a seemingly endless selection of romantic towns and historical sights. For the more energetic there is also an excellent network of cycle paths around the lake.</p>]]></thingsToDo>
